<p>The server also supports a basic HTTP REST signalling mechanism for WebRTC peers. See these examples, <a target="_blank" href="webrtc.html">Dual Peer Connection</a> and
   <a target="_blank" href="webrtc-solo.html">Single Peer Connection</a>.</p>

